		<h4>Books by this Author</h4>
		<h6>Books by John Grisham at BookBrowse</h6>
		
		
					<a href="https://www.bookbrowse.com/bb_briefs/detail/index.cfm/ezine_preview_number/7940/the-racketeer jacket"><img src="/images/previews_images/0385535147.jpg" alt="The Racketeer jacket" class="img_left"/></a>
	        	
